<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11169</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17608</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>黑雨大王双手抱头坐在悬崖边上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17608</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21337</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他低着头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21337</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27492</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好久不见，黑雨大王！” 一个妖怪走上悬崖说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27492</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29130</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你怎么了？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29130</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35979</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>黑雨大王叹了一口气：“我正在准备晚饭，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35979</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41631</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孙悟空突然来打我，我不得不逃出来了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41631</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>48417</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那个妖怪摇了摇头：“为什么你要让孙悟空这样欺负？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>48417</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>黑雨大王惊讶地抬起头：“孙悟空真的太强大了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61211</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嘁！” 那个妖怪挥了挥手，“你不应该离开你的山。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61211</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64030</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>黑雨大王点了点头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64030</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69799</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果是我，肯定不会让孙悟空欺负。” 那个妖怪说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69799</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75814</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>黑雨大王握紧了拳头：“我也不会！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75814</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82566</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“八戒在哪儿？” 悟空瞪着迅翼，举起了金箍棒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82566</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87802</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>迅翼看起来很害怕：“他在另一个世界！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87802</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92783</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空放下金箍棒：“另一个世界？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92783</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96680</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他是怎么过去的？” 唐僧问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96680</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100639</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我打开了传送门。” 迅翼说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100639</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107832</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“猪八戒打黑雨大王时被绊了一下，掉进了传送门。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107832</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110617</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不明白。” 悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110617</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115164</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你为什么要打开去另一个世界的门？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115164</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119299</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“黑雨大王让我打开的。” 迅翼说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119299</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126032</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那里有一个强大的女神仙，黑雨大王想请她帮忙。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126032</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130115</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“请她帮什么忙？” 唐僧问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130115</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139089</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>迅翼垂下眼睛：“她，嗯……可以打败孙悟空。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139089</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142188</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么？” 悟空握紧拳头，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142188</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148241</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没人能打败我！如果见到她，我会除掉她！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148241</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152950</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“悟空，先别管那个女神仙。” 唐僧说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152950</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157254</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们要找到八戒。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157254</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161479</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“师父说得对。” 悟空看着迅翼，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161479</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166615</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“告诉我该怎么打开传送门。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166615</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>迅翼把咒语教给悟空。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171502</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178149</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她刚说完，悟空就举起金箍棒，迅翼向后退去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178149</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187337</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“悟空，你要做什么？” 唐僧说，“她帮了我们！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187337</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192965</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“师父，她是妖怪，我要除掉她。” 悟空说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192965</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198551</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对不起。” 迅翼说，“我本来是一只普通的鸟，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198551</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206511</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>是黑雨大王抓了我，把我变成了妖怪！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>206511</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215462</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空叹了口气，放下了金箍棒：“如果你真的想变好，就去普陀山吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215462</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219017</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“观音菩萨那里吗？” 迅翼问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219017</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227060</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空点了点头：“去做观音菩萨的弟子，她会好好儿教你的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227060</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232683</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>迅翼低头行礼：“我会去的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232683</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239397</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后拍着翅膀飞走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239397</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242679</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空念出咒语，传送门打开，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242679</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246961</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>出现了一座有很多高楼的城市。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246961</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>251822</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧睁大眼睛：“哇！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>251822</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>255660</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“师父，你们在这里等着。” 悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>255660</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260416</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我会尽快找到八戒，带他回来。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260416</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>268897</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空跳进传送门，门在他身后消失了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>268897</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>272021</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧坐了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>272021</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>275808</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“师父，您看起来很累。” 悟净说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>275808</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>282090</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我去看看马，您先休息一会儿。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>282090</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>289594</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧闭上眼睛休息，但是很快就听到了脚步声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>289594</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>298337</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“悟净，你这么快就回来了？” 他睁开眼睛，然后尖叫起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>298337</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>305207</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>黑雨大王笑了笑：“又见面了，唐僧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>